      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-06-04T15:02:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There are a lot of potential problems which this does not account for.  I\u0027d recommend using git.Checkout.Update() instead: https://skia.googlesource.com/buildbot/+/master/go/git/checkout.go#89",
      "range": {
